{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"959","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"育嬰留停新制7月上路 勞工須10天前預告雇主","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>最新更新：2021/05/14 11:05</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><img alt='' src='http://www.ctspcsr.com.tw/user_files/news_files/%E8%82%B2%E5%AC%B0.jpg' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 100%;' /></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>育嬰留職停薪新制將於7月上路。勞動部預告相關法規指出，勞工申請育嬰留停須提前10天預告雇主。（示意圖/圖取自Pixabay圖庫）</span></p>\n\n<hr style='box-sizing: content-box; border-radius: 0px; height: 1px; margin: 20px 0px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), transparent); color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;' />\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;'>（中央社記者吳欣紜台北14日電）育嬰留職停薪新制將於7月上路，勞工申請育嬰留停須提前預告雇主，勞動部近日預告相關法規，參考離職、解僱預告期規定，將日期訂為10天前。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>現行法規規定，受僱者申請育嬰留停，應事先以書面向雇主提出，而育嬰留停期間，每次以不少於6個月為原則，要低於6個月須與雇主協商。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>行政院日前拍板放寬育嬰留停相關規定，包含雙親可同時申請育嬰留停及津貼，請育嬰假時也不需一次就請6個月，但不得少於30天，少於6個月的次數以2次為限，且須提前預告雇主。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>勞動部後續啟動法制作業程序，近日預告修正「育嬰留職停薪實施辦法」部分條文修正草案，明定勞工申請育嬰留停時，須於10天前以書面向雇主提出，10日是參考現行勞動法規中離職、資遣及解僱等預告天數研議。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>據行政院公報，法案預告期7天，如果有意見或修正建議者可陳述意見；如果無相關意見，法規預計7月1 日上路。（編輯：李明宗）1100514</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>資料來源:&nbsp;<a href='https://www.cna.com.tw/news/ahel/202105140043.aspx' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 158, 184); text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px !important;'>https://www.cna.com.tw/news/ahel/202105140043.aspx</a></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2021-05-21","clk_count":"203"}},"__N_SSG":true}